        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A large, stylized symbol of an eye adorns the top of this wooden staff, representing the watchful eye of the divine powers. The bearer of the staff can guide and protect, seeing bounties and tragedies that could befall them in the future.</p>\n<p>When wielding this staff, you gain a +1 item bonus on Survival checks to Sense Direction or Subsist, and to Religion checks to Recall Knowledge.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Guidance]{Guidance}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Light]{Light}</li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Bless]{Bless}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Create Water]{Create Water}</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Augury]{Augury}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Create Food]{Create Food}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.See Invisibility]{See Invisibility}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Status]{Status}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+1 item bonus to Survival checks to Sense Direction or Subsist,</li>\n<li>+1 item bonus to Religion checks to Recall Knowledge</li>\n</ul>"
